          1 of 13        


 






Celebrate summer with a backyard BBQ, potluck picnic, pool party -- there are so many opportunities for fun with these must-have supplies from Martha!
 
Heat up the Grill
Stock up on charcoal, because it’s officially grilling season! Celebrate the flavors of summer with Martha & Marley Spoon, Martha’s meal kit delivery service, which brings fresh ingredients and creative recipes to your door each week. Choose from recipes like Indian Pork Burgers, Greek Veggie Skewers, and Steak Salad. With the menu planned out and grocery shopping done for you, you’ll have more time to relax with family and friends!







Order Your Meal Kit 












Pinterest





Facebook










          2 of 13        


The Tools of Summer 






Once your Martha & Marley Spoon meal kit is ordered, make sure you have the right grilling tools for the job. Shop for tongs, a grilling thermometer, skewers, grill baskets, and more from the Martha Stewart Collection™, only at Macy’s.


              Photography: Macy’s            






Shop These Grilling Tools 












Pinterest





Facebook










          3 of 13        


Chill the Wine 






Did you know that adding salt to an ice bath will lower the water’s freezing point, in turn chilling the contents faster? This method comes in handy for chilling white wine on a warm summer day; simply add the right bottles for the occasion! Shop Martha Stewart Wine Co., Martha’s new online shop dedicated to helping you discover wines from around the world. Choose from individual bottles of reds and whites, warm-weather rosés, curated wine packs, and a wine club membership.







Place Your Order 












Pinterest





Facebook










          4 of 13        


Keep Drinks Cold 






Instead of using a cumbersome (and unsightly) cooler, set out a beverage bucket with an assortment of cold drinks to keep party guests refreshed. Liven up the plain exterior with a fun design or pattern created with Martha Stewart Multi-Surface Acrylic Craft Paint.   







Craft This Beverage Bucket 












Pinterest





Facebook










          5 of 13        


Use Carefree Drinkware 






For outdoor parties with a relaxed atmosphere, eliminate the worry of broken glass by using drinkware made from durable materials like acrylic. This cup and pitcher set from the Martha Stewart Collection only at Macy’s is shatter-resistant and adds a pop of color to the table.


              Photography: Macy's            






Shop This Cup & Pitcher Set 












Pinterest





Facebook










          6 of 13        


Arrange a Self-Serve Drink Station 






Keep the party casual with a self-serve drink station so you’re free to mingle with friends and family instead of playing bartender. This acrylic drink dispenser from the Martha Stewart Collection™, only at Macy’s, holds 2.5 gallons of your favorite juice, tea, or cocktail.


              Photography: Macy's            






Shop This Drink Dispenser 






