          7 of 13        


Sweeten the Menu 






With a seemingly-endless supply of hot dogs, potato chips, sugary beverages, and other traditional party fare, it’s not surprising dessert may sound overindulgent. Trade store-bought desserts for healthier homemade treats from Martha’s newest cookbook, A New Way to Bake. Learn to transform classic recipes with modern ingredients, like whole-grain flours and natural sweeteners, for sweet treats everyone will enjoy.


              Photography: Reprinted from A New Way to Bake            






Purchase This Cookbook 












