Facebook










          8 of 13        


Display Fresh Blooms 






The weather’s warm and the flowers are blooming! Show off your garden’s best in creative vases placed around your party space. Craft these colorful mason jars using Martha Stewart Multi-Surface Satin Acrylic Craft Paint and Gilding Sheets.







Craft These Jars 












