Keep Utensils Organized 






If you’re planning a buffet or self-serve assortment of appetizers, you’ll want to have plenty of flatware on hand. Keep the table organized with these customizable utensil holders made from terracotta pots. Transform the plain planters with Martha Stewart Chalkboard Paint and Adhesive Stencils.


              Photography: Mike Krautter            






