Go Fresh & Colorful 






The Summer Sweets line from the Martha Stewart Collection™, only at Macy’s, radiates fun in the sun! The assortment features durable materials like melamine and acrylic, seasonal patterns of pineapples and watermelons, and an array of bright colors. Your serveware will be perfectly-coordinated, and the fun style feels fresh and inviting.


              Photography: Macy’s            






