Brighten Up the Table 






Accent woven placemats with Martha Stewart Acrylic Satin Paint in bright summer colors like Magenta Rose, Wild Salmon, and Pea Shoot. Create a border, color block stripes, or your own unique pattern. After the meal, gently wipe them clean for their next use.


              Photography: Andrew Ingalls            






