Let the Games Begin 






Keep the kids (and young-at-heart adults) entertained with an easy-to-play game of paddleball. Customize a set of blank paddles with Martha Stewart Multi-Surface Acrylic Craft Paint and Stencils. Pay tribute to your favorite summer treat, create a colorful ombré effect, or come up with your own unique design!







