          13 of 13        


Splash Around  






Whether you’re hosting a pool party, backyard picnic, or deck-side BBQ, festive beach towels are a must. This sweet treat of a towel is made from plush cotton and is part of the Martha Stewart Collection™, only at Macy’s. It comes in a variety of seasonal patterns like pineapples, flamingos, and colorful stripes.


