Martha Stewart - Wikipedia






















 







Martha Stewart

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

This is the latest accepted revision, reviewed on 6 July 2017.




					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the actress born in 1922, see Martha Stewart (actress).


Martha Stewart



Stewart at the 2011 Tribeca Film Festival Vanity Fair party



Born
Martha Helen Kostyra
(1941-08-03) August 3, 1941 (age 75)
Jersey City, New Jersey, U.S.


Residence
Katonah, New York,
