 Martha Stewart
(II)


 
Actress |
 
Producer





Martha Stewart was born on August 3, 1941 in Nutley, New Jersey, USA as Martha Helen Kostyra. She is an actress and producer, known for Martha Stewart Living (1991), Martha (2005) and Comedy Central Roast of Justin Bieber (2015). She was previously married to Andrew Stewart.            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

August 3, 
     
1941

            in
            Nutley, New Jersey, USA





